<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="no">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Text Relay<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Step free access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentbb4c0acbfea14f438a4221267d60858e">
</div>
<p>Step free access - both our main patient entrances are step free and also from our main car park areas there are no steps – access from the lower rear car park involves steps</p>
