<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="no">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent382ef810548743bf851faa8cb4b8ca46">
</div>
<p>The Trust has a chaplaincy department to enable patients, relatives, carers and staff to receive religious, spiritual and pastoral support appropriate to their individual needs. <br/><br/>The Trust employs one full time Chaplain (Church of England), one Free Church, and one Roman Catholic minister at the District Hospital in addition to a part time for each of the Community Hospitals. <br/><br/>The faith services can be contacted on: 01271 322362</p>
